## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible strategies for environmental protection. The information is subject to change as new research and technologies emerge. Additionally, the effectiveness of these strategies can vary based on geographic and socio-economic contexts. Further research and localized studies are recommended to tailor these strategies to specific communities and environments.

